    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major features and electronics functioning as they should. It drives smoothly and represents a reliable option for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that has been looked after.",
